</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="97" pageNumber="697" type="activity">
<paragraph blockId="97.[1360,2566,2534,3157]" pageId="97" pageNumber="697">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1360,1598,2926,2960]" pageId="97" pageNumber="697">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
The Manus Island Mosaic-tailed Rat seems to be a largely arboreal species.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection box="[1362,2301,3010,3039]" pageId="97" pageNumber="697" type="biology_ecology">
<paragraph blockId="97.[1360,2566,2534,3157]" box="[1362,2301,3010,3039]" pageId="97" pageNumber="697">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1362,2062,3010,3039]" pageId="97" pageNumber="697">Movements, Home range and Social organization.</emphasis>
